To create ospf
- router ospf 1
to spread a route using it
network NETADDRESS WILDCARD MASK area 0



troubleshooting
the ports on each of 2 connecting routers need to be on the same network, meaning both ip addresses need to be

to remove ospf or route
no router ospf 1
no NETADDRESS WILDCARD area 0


authentication

plaintext

interface the port
R1(config-if)#ip ospf authentication-key secret
R1(config-if)#ip ospf authentication

do this on all ports using ospf
